<i>noun</i>: 의자 [의자], 걸상 [걸ː쌍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>의자 [의자]</dt><br>
<dd>chair; stool</dd><br>
<dd>사람이 엉덩이와 허벅지를 대고 걸터앉는 데 쓰는 기구.</dd><br>
<dd>An apparatus made for a person to sit with his/her hip and thighs placed on it.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>걸상 [걸ː쌍]</dt><br>
<dd>chair; stool</dd><br>
<dd>사람이 앉기 위해 만든 기구.</dd><br>
<dd>An apparatus made for a person to sit on.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>